Those are the big digs
we did while you were gone.

762
00:37:01.850 --> 00:37:03.933
- It's a good week.
- Yeah. I think so.

763
00:37:04.017 --> 00:37:05.808
And they were getting ready

764
00:37:05.975 --> 00:37:08.017
to put in the last caisson
up in the Money Pit.

765
00:37:08.183 --> 00:37:09.895
- and it's about ready to go.
- That's good news.

766
00:37:09.975 --> 00:37:12.725
- Yeah. - Anyway.
that's it. That's my report.

767
00:37:12.808 --> 00:37:14.600
So. to me.

768
00:37:14.767 --> 00:37:17.433
there's always been concern
in this room

769
00:37:17.642 --> 00:37:19.183
that the treasure
had been found.

770
00:37:22.017 --> 00:37:24.100
But you think about it.
if this really is

771
00:37:24.267 --> 00:37:26.725
a treasure coin from
the depths of the Money Pit.

772
00:37:26.933 --> 00:37:28.392
then where are they?

773
00:37:30.933 --> 00:37:33.350
- The Money Pit.
- In the Money Pit.

774
00:37:34.475 --> 00:37:35.933
That shows it. right?

775
00:37:37.142 --> 00:37:38.437
Well. let's go find something

776
00:37:38.517 --> 00:37:40.392
very special.

777
00:37:40.558 --> 00:37:42.183
The sky's the limit.

778
00:37:43.058 --> 00:37:44.738
- Let's go look.
- All right. okay.

779
00:37:45.975 --> 00:37:47.975
Let's get to work.

780
00:37:51.683 --> 00:37:53.475
In the heart of the Money Pit.

781
00:37:53.642 --> 00:37:54.767
Hey. Rick.

782
00:37:54.975 --> 00:37:57.100
- Hey.
- Hey.

783
00:37:57.308 --> 00:37:59.267
- New hole. fresh start?
- Fresh start.

784
00:37:59.433 --> 00:38:01.308
In the Money Pit area.

785
00:38:01.475 --> 00:38:05.558
Rick arrives as representatives
from SB Canada and ROC Equipment

786
00:38:05.642 --> 00:38:07.350
are about to break ground

787
00:38:07.517 --> 00:38:12.017
on the team's final shaft
of the year... Money Pit-1.

788
00:38:12.183 --> 00:38:14.100
This last hole...
Money Pit-1...

789
00:38:14.308 --> 00:38:16.475
might be one of the best chances

790
00:38:16.642 --> 00:38:20.100
to get deep in an area where
we haven't explored at depth.

791
00:38:20.225 --> 00:38:22.433
So. Steve.
can you put us on the map?

792
00:38:22.642 --> 00:38:25.183
Yes. we're dead center
between these three caissons.

793
00:38:25.350 --> 00:38:26.937
And that's where
we've had all the success...

794
00:38:27.017 --> 00:38:28.642
the bottom
of the solution channel.

795
00:38:28.808 --> 00:38:30.725
where it's showing
signs of silver.

796
00:38:30.892 --> 00:38:32.392
And we're not far
from those areas.

797
00:38:34.933 --> 00:38:37.100
The MP-1 shaft is located

798
00:38:37.267 --> 00:38:40.017
less than ten feet
from the Karma-1

799
00:38:40.183 --> 00:38:44.475
and Top Pocket Find shafts
that were dug several weeks ago.

800
00:38:44.642 --> 00:38:47.017
During those excavations.

801
00:38:47.225 --> 00:38:50.058
where the highest traces
of silver have been detected

802
00:38:50.267 --> 00:38:52.850
more than 200 feet deep
in the solution channel.

803
00:38:53.058 --> 00:38:56.017
artifacts and pieces of wood

804
00:38:56.183 --> 00:38:58.600
that may have been related
to the original Money Pit

805
00:38:58.725 --> 00:39:00.600
were brought to the surface.

806
00:39:00.725 --> 00:39:02.475
This is a very good location.

807
00:39:02.642 --> 00:39:05.767
We have... stand every
good chance to be successful.

808
00:39:05.933 --> 00:39:08.642
- Yep.
- We don't want metal finds.

809
00:39:08.808 --> 00:39:11.142
We want to find treasure.

810
00:39:11.308 --> 00:39:13.558
- Yeah.
- And answers to the mystery.

811
00:39:13.725 --> 00:39:16.600
-Brilliant. -If we're gonna
find the treasure. to me.

812
00:39:16.767 --> 00:39:19.058
- this is our best chance.
- I hope you got your boots on.

813
00:39:19.183 --> 00:39:22.767
Rick. 'cause we're gonna be
knee-deep in artifacts.

814
00:39:22.975 --> 00:39:24.600
Everything we found this year.

815
00:39:24.725 --> 00:39:26.850
everything we found
in all the previous years

816
00:39:27.017 --> 00:39:30.933
indicates that this
could be the spot

817
00:39:31.058 --> 00:39:34.058
where the treasure fell
into the solution channel.

818
00:39:34.225 --> 00:39:36.767
This is our last caisson
this year

819
00:39:36.975 --> 00:39:39.267
but also the best shot.

820
00:39:39.433 --> 00:39:41.058
What say you guys?

821
00:39:41.225 --> 00:39:42.562
- Hey.
- This looking like a good spot?

822
00:39:42.642 --> 00:39:44.058
- It is.
- I love it.

823
00:39:44.183 --> 00:39:46.017
Wouldn't be anywhere else

824
00:39:46.183 --> 00:39:48.975
but right here.
going through Money Pit spoils.

825
00:39:49.142 --> 00:39:50.782
- You're having fun.
- It's brilliant.

826
00:39:52.350 --> 00:39:54.142
We have silver in the water

827
00:39:54.308 --> 00:39:58.433
that is consistent with
the 14th century Portuguese coin

828
00:39:58.600 --> 00:40:02.142
that almost certainly
came from the Money Pit.

829
00:40:02.350 --> 00:40:06.433
I think we are building
a very excellent case

830
00:40:06.642 --> 00:40:09.225
that old-world treasure

831
00:40:09.392 --> 00:40:13.558
that is deemed to be at depth
in the Money Pit is still there.

832
00:40:13.725 --> 00:40:15.225
And now. in MP-1.

833
00:40:15.392 --> 00:40:18.392
we are on the cusp
of proving it to the most...

834
00:40:18.558 --> 00:40:20.600
how shall we say...
hardened skeptic.

835
00:40:21.642 --> 00:40:24.183
I really want to know
what's way down deep.

836
00:40:24.308 --> 00:40:26.183
Here we go. Showtime.

837
00:40:27.975 --> 00:40:29.517
Marty has said many times

838
00:40:29.725 --> 00:40:32.100
that the story of Oak Island
started in the Money Pit

839
00:40:32.308 --> 00:40:33.767
and it will end
in the Money Pit.

840
00:40:33.933 --> 00:40:35.850
Why not name it Money Pit-1?

841
00:40:35.975 --> 00:40:37.600
Let's find this.

842
00:40:37.808 --> 00:40:39.600
Ooh. I like the look
of that material.

843
00:40:39.767 --> 00:40:41.142
Treasure on deck.

844
00:40:41.350 --> 00:40:42.767
- Yep.
- Let's get stuck in.

845
00:40:42.933 --> 00:40:44.600
I'll go join 'em for luck.

846
00:40:44.767 --> 00:40:46.683
Okay.

847
00:40:46.850 --> 00:40:48.183
Keep your fingers crossed.

848
00:40:48.350 --> 00:40:50.600
So far this year.

849
00:40:50.683 --> 00:40:53.850
the team has unearthed
discoveries on Oak Island

850
00:40:53.975 --> 00:40:57.725
and made revelations
across the ocean

851
00:40:57.850 --> 00:41:01.850
that suggest a valuable
and potentially sacred treasure

852
00:41:02.058 --> 00:41:04.683
was buried long ago
in the Money Pit.

853
00:41:06.850 --> 00:41:09.433
Now they are digging

854
00:41:09.600 --> 00:41:13.433
where all of this
compelling evidence is pointing.

855
00:41:14.475 --> 00:41:16.100
Others have searched here

856
00:41:16.267 --> 00:41:18.933
only to be thwarted by forces

857
00:41:19.100 --> 00:41:21.808
that are perhaps beyond nature.

858
00:41:21.975 --> 00:41:24.558
But for the Laginas
and their team...

859
00:41:25.642 --> 00:41:29.308
a different destiny
may be waiting...

860
00:41:31.517 --> 00:41:32.725
below.

